thread.title: Joseph Cinque
thread.title_full: MirrorMate Frames reviewed by Joseph Cinque

author: Joseph Cinque
title: Joseph Cinque
text: Order 2 sets for 2 oversized bathroom mirrors, came when I requested, easy to assemble if you take your time, let joint glue dry overnight to be safe, easy to install. I made a mistake on 1 set but able to get frame off with fishing line and Mirrormate sent we new tape very quickly. Great company and product!!!
